item.title: Overview
item.description: Introduction Hello! Welcome! My name is Evan Tyo and I am a software engineer that currently specializes in web developement. I have a Bachelor of Science in Computer Science and have been working in the field for 2.5 years. In a professional setting, I’ve mainly worked with JavaScript, Node, and Express. I’ve also become familiar using AWS, Bitbucket, Confluence, Bamboo, Git, GitHub, and GitHub Workflows. Additionally, I’ve had educational projects that have utilized Java, C#, Python, SQL, PostgreSQL, MongoDB, GraphQL, .
